data.description: Welcome to 13415 Star Creek Ln, located in the coveted master planned community of Lakes of Savannah. This inviting and spacious all brick 1-story home offers a split floorplan, high ceilings and an abundance of natural light throughout. Enjoy the two spacious living areas, formal dining and open floor plan made for entertainment. The backyard offers privacy and tranquility with a covered patio, oversized lot and no back neighbors. The recently replaced AC will keep you cool throughout the hot Texas summers and you can relax on the patio with surround sound to elevate your entertainment experience. Indulge in the luxury of a water softener system, providing you with the highest quality water throughout the house. Unwind in the upgraded walk-in shower designed to elevate your daily bathing experience to new heights of relaxation and comfort. Embrace a lifestyle of convenience by enjoying the community clubhouse, recreation centers, resort-style pool, splashpad and pocket parks!
